FIGS. 2 and 3 show cross-sectional views of the formation of a gate of the prior art;


FIG. 4 through 11 show the layers and structures used to form a polymetal silicide conductor/gate of the present invention; and


FIG. 12 is a flow diagram of a process of making a polymetal silicide conductor/gate.
